      <w type="h1">Overview</w>
<w type="p">Components and options for laying out your LCUI project, including wrapping containers, a simple grid system.</w>
<w type="h2">Containers</w>
<w type="p">Containers are the most basic layout element LCUI and are required when using our default grid system. Choose from a fixed-width container or fluid-width.</w>
<w type="p">While containers can be nested, most layouts do not require a nested container.</w>

